# Cross-Persona Comparison

|  | Persona 1: Ritual Optimizer | Persona 2: Considered Indulger | Persona 3: Time-Poor Standard-Keeper |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Core tension** | Indulgence vs. performance | Pleasure vs. integrity | Speed vs. quality |
| **Discovery channel** | TikTok, Reddit, micro-creator | Instagram, Pinterest, in-store | Group chat, grocery delivery, newsletter |
| **Conversion trigger** | Format fit in existing routine | Sensory storytelling + in-store impulse | Peer recommendation + frictionless purchase |
| **Primary objection** | "Is this actually different?" | "$14 for peanut butter?" | "Will my household actually use this?" |
| **Decision maker** | Mostly solo, validates with data | Solo + partner aesthetic veto | Household unit, peer-validated |
| **Loyalty driver** | Routine lock-in | WOM + aesthetics | Auto-reorder / Subscribe & Save |
| **Best channel** | DTC, Amazon, TikTok | Instagram, specialty retail | Amazon, Instacart, Whole Foods |
| **Ad tone** | Clinical-cool, proof-forward | Sensory, playful, no health preaching | Utility-forward, no condescension |

