# Strategic Implications for Spoonless

**Persona 1** is your early adopter and credibility builder — they write the Reddit threads that Persona 2 and 3 eventually find. Win them first. Invest in clean DTC experience, strong ingredient transparency, and micro-creator seeding.

**Persona 2** is your volume driver — they have the highest WOM coefficient and respond to aesthetic and occasion marketing. This is your Instagram and in-store play. The bottle design needs to do work here.

**Persona 3** is your retention engine — once locked in, they Subscribe & Save and send 3–5 referrals without being asked. The path to them runs through Amazon, Instacart, and parenting communities. Make the Subscribe & Save experience frictionless and you own their pantry slot.